349
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,550
January 2nd.

350
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,400
A Capricorn?

351
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:21,550
I'm getting emotional.

352
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,070
Did you get my permission

353
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:24,000
