354
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,510
Dude, this is a surprise.

355
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:26,400
Why aren't you showing some appreciation?

356
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,000
Dude,

357
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:27,790
