536
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,480
Let go of me!

537
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:39,960
Go away!

538
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:41,680
My foot.

539
00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:44,920
Go after her!

