558
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:36,830
Watch out!

559
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,240
Watch out, Sang Yan.

560
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:53,510
Open the door!

561
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:00,960
Open the door!

562
00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:05,830
Watch out, Sang Yan.

563
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:07,480
Stop!

